tilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Verve</h2>\n<blockquote><p>A different and powerful web experience.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/verve-highstyle-wordpress-theme/14758884\">Purchase Verve</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Construction</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Construction is a WordPress business theme. It is focused on building websites in the construction company niches.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/construction-wordpress-theme/14802222\">Purchase Construction</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Kalium</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Kalium is a creative theme which works with Visual Composer, Portfolio Type plugin and  includes Revolution + Layer Slider.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/kalium-creative-theme-for-professionals/10860525\">Purchase Kalium</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Valeria</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Valeria is a Fully Responsive WordPress Theme designed for Professional Photographer and any other creative people with a very Minimal and Clean Design.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/valeria-photography-wordpress-theme/15434660\">Purchase Valeria</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=vHZgaJ6lP0c:NBaeXsa8XLY:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=vHZgaJ6lP0c:NBaeXsa8XLY:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=vHZgaJ6lP0c:NBaeXsa8XLY:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=vHZgaJ6lP0c:NBaeXsa8XLY:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=vHZgaJ6lP0c:NBaeXsa8XLY:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=vHZgaJ6lP0c:NBaeXsa8XLY:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/vHZgaJ6lP0c\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://wpml.org/2016/06/compatible-portfolio-themes-jun-2016/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://wpml.org/2016/06/compatible-portfolio-themes-jun-2016/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"Translate Photo Gallery Plugin Using WPML\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/E81vZAYDflc/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://wpml.org/2016/06/translate-photo-gallery-plugin-using-wpml/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 20 Jun 2016 15:57:06 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Compatibility\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"https://wpml.org/?p=920249\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:356:\"Introduction Photo Gallery is one of the great plugins to create your image galleries in WordPress. Its integration with WPML will allow you to translate your galleries. What you will need Photo Gallery plugin (version 2.1.31 or above). A recent version of WPML (version 3.3.8 or above) and the String Translation add-on. WordPress (version 4.5.2 [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Mohamed Khafaja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11989:\"<h2><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-924830 size-full\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Photo-Gallery.png\" alt=\"Photo Gallery\" width=\"680\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Photo-Gallery.png 680w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Photo-Gallery-150x45.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Photo-Gallery-300x90.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /></h2>\n<h2>Introduction</h2>\n<p>Photo Gallery is one of the great plugins to create your image galleries in WordPress. Its integration with WPML will allow you to translate your galleries.</p>\n<h2>What you will need</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/photo-gallery/\">Photo Gallery</a> plugin (version 2.1.31 or above).</li>\n<li>A recent version of <a href=\"https://wpml.org/purchase/\">WPML</a> (version 3.3.8 or above) and the String Translation add-on.</li>\n<li>WordPress (version 4.5.2 or above).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Essential resources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>WPML’s <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/getting-started-guide/\">Getting Started Guide</a> will help you set up WPML in a few minutes.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"https://web-dorado.com/wordpress-gallery/installing.html\">Photo Gallery step-by-step guide</a> provides detailed instructions on how to create, customize and insert galleries into pages.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Getting started</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Install and activate the WPML plugin.</li>\n<li>Install and activate the Photo Gallery plugin.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Translation</h2>\n<p>We will be creating two galleries: one will be inserted in our default language gallery page and the other into our secondary language gallery page.</p>\n<h2>Create the image gallery (for the default and secondary languages)</h2>\n<p><iframe width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/VPwP3Ng8czg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<ol>\n<li>On your WordPress dashboard, navigate to “Photo Gallery” &gt; “Add Galleries/Images” and click on the “Add new” button.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-new-gallery.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-920414\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-new-gallery-300x108.png\" alt=\"Add new gallery\" width=\"500\" height=\"180\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-new-gallery-300x108.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-new-gallery-150x54.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-new-gallery-768x277.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-new-gallery-1024x369.png 1024w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-new-gallery.png 1335w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Fill in the “Name” field and the “Description” field (in case you want to add a description to your gallery).</li>\n<li>Click on the “Add images” button.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Gallery-name-ana-description.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-920365\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Gallery-name-ana-description-300x125.png\" alt=\"Gallery name ana description\" width=\"500\" height=\"209\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Gallery-name-ana-description-300x125.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Gallery-name-ana-description-150x63.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Gallery-name-ana-description-768x321.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Gallery-name-ana-description-1024x428.png 1024w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Gallery-name-ana-description.png 1334w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Click on the “Upload files” button and choose the images that you want to add to your gallery.</li>\n<li>Select the images that you want to add to your gallery or click on the “Select all” button.</li>\n<li>Click on the “Add selected images to gallery” button; add your images titles, description and tags.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-selected-images-to-gallery.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-920378\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-selected-images-to-gallery-300x188.png\" alt=\"Add selected images to gallery\" width=\"500\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-selected-images-to-gallery-300x188.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-selected-images-to-gallery-150x94.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-selected-images-to-gallery.png 715w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>Click on the “Save” button. With that, we have created the image gallery that will be inserted into our default language (in this tutorial it is “English”) gallery page.</li>\n<li>Repeat the same process to create the secondary language gallery (in our case, it is French). Remember to add your translated textual content when creating the gallery.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Create and translate the gallery page</h2>\n<p><iframe width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2v37thlGvIA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<ol>\n<ol>\n<li>Navigate to “Pages” &gt; “Add New”.</li>\n<li>Add the page title (Buildings gallery).</li>\n<li>Click on the “Insert photo gallery” icon <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-920343\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-gallery-icon.png\" alt=\"Insert gallery icon\" width=\"30\" height=\"23\" /> .</li>\n</ol>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-default-language-gallery-page.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-920400\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-default-language-gallery-page-300x135.png\" alt=\"Add default language gallery page\" width=\"500\" height=\"226\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-default-language-gallery-page-300x135.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-default-language-gallery-page-150x68.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-default-language-gallery-page-768x347.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-default-language-gallery-page-1024x462.png 1024w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-default-language-gallery-page.png 1331w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<ol>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>From the gallery drop down menu, select the first gallery that we have created (in our case, it is “Buildings gallery”) and click on the “Insert” button.</li>\n</ol>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-default-language-gallery.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-920427\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-default-language-gallery-300x160.png\" alt=\"Insert default language gallery\" width=\"500\" height=\"266\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-default-language-gallery-300x160.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-default-language-gallery-150x80.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-default-language-gallery-768x409.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-default-language-gallery.png 985w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<ol>\n<ol>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>Click on the “Publish” button.</li>\n<li>Click on the <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-919955\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Plus-icon.png\" alt=\"Plus icon\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /> icon, found in the language meta-box on the right, to translate the gallery page.</li>\n</ol>\n</ol>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-translation-to-the-gallery-page.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-920445 size-full\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-translation-to-the-gallery-page.png\" alt=\"Add translation to the gallery page\" width=\"247\" height=\"210\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-translation-to-the-gallery-page.png 247w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-translation-to-the-gallery-page-150x128.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 247px) 100vw, 247px\" /></a></p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>Click on the “copy content from English” button and edit the loaded text with your translation in the title and the body.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-your-translated-text-to-the-gallery-page.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-920456\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-your-translated-text-to-the-gallery-page-300x135.png\" alt=\"Add your translated text to the gallery page\" width=\"500\" height=\"224\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-your-translated-text-to-the-gallery-page-300x135.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-your-translated-text-to-the-gallery-page-150x67.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-your-translated-text-to-the-gallery-page-768x345.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-your-translated-text-to-the-gallery-page-1024x460.png 1024w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Add-your-translated-text-to-the-gallery-page.png 1328w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li>Delete the gallery shortcode and click on the “Insert photo gallery” icon <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-920343\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-gallery-icon.png\" alt=\"Insert gallery icon\" width=\"30\" height=\"23\" /> . Choose the gallery that we created for the secondary language (FR-Buildings).</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-your-secondary-language-gallery.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-920472\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-your-secondary-language-gallery-300x159.png\" alt=\"Insert your secondary language gallery\" width=\"500\" height=\"264\" srcset=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-your-secondary-language-gallery-300x159.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-your-secondary-language-gallery-150x79.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-your-secondary-language-gallery-768x406.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Insert-your-secondary-language-gallery.png 986w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<ol start=\"9\">\n<li>Click on the publish button.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Now, we have loaded each instance of the gallery that we created into the right page and will display the correct gallery on each of them.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=E81vZAYDflc:sMgGMtQxisw:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=E81vZAYDflc:sMgGMtQxisw:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=E81vZAYDflc:sMgGMtQxisw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=E81vZAYDflc:sMgGMtQxisw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=E81vZAYDflc:sMgGMtQxisw:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=E81vZAYDflc:sMgGMtQxisw:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/E81vZAYDflc\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s