9/Results-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2824,1,'2015-09-08 23:00:14','2015-09-08 23:00:14','','Solution','','inherit','open','closed','','solution-2','','','2015-09-08 23:00:14','2015-09-08 23:00:14','',2668,'http://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Solution.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2825,1,'2015-09-08 23:01:27','2015-09-08 23:01:27','','Problem','','inherit','open','closed','','problem','','','2015-09-08 23:01:27','2015-09-08 23:01:27','',2668,'http://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Problem.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2826,1,'2015-09-08 23:01:58','2015-09-08 23:01:58','','Problem-vintage','','inherit','open','closed','','problem-vintage','','','2015-09-08 23:01:58','2015-09-08 23:01:58','',0,'http://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Problem-vintage.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2827,1,'2015-09-08 23:03:11','2015-09-08 23:03:11','','Results-3','','inherit','open','closed','','results-3-2','','','2015-09-08 23:03:11','2015-09-08 23:03:11','',2668,'http://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Results-3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2828,1,'2015-08-03 23:09:40','2015-08-03 23:09:40','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">LOOKING TO THE FUTURE OF MACHINE AUTOMATION</h2>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Industry leader in machine-vision systems prepares for global expansion with its best-in-class technology.</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"20\" padding_bottom=\"20\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1442861846634{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>THE RVT PLATFORM</h2>\r\nRobotic VISION Technologies (RVT), an independent software and support services company, develops software products that enable robots and other automated machines to “see, think, and do.” Advanced machine vision is a key factor for robotic systems to become more precise, reliable, and efficient. RVT’s software platform for vision-guided robotics supports applications in multiple industries, including automotive, materials handling, bottling, inspection, and general manufacturing.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"3040\" img_size=\"600x399\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" margin_bottom=\"-40\" padding_top=\"-40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2989\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1442862639554{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1463770070531{margin-right: 10px !important;margin-left: 20px !important;}\"]\r\n<h2>PARTNERSHIP WITH IDF</h2>\r\nRVT’s technology leadership and U.S.-based industry success positions the company for global growth. RVT partnered with IDF to expedite progress toward an increased international presence. Through this strategic partnership, RVT will gain access to IDF’s global network of inventors to collaborate on new robotics inventions. IDF will also help strengthen RVT’s existing patent portfolio and will introduce new markets and customers to RVT technology and software products.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" fancy_edge=\"corner_down\" fancy_edge_size=\"lg\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" fancy_edge_t_color=\"#0e73a3\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441133988315{margin-top: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>GLOBAL OPPORTUNITIES</h2>\r\nThe future is bright for RVT as the use of robotic technologies rapidly expands into new industries and applications, creating demand for advanced machine vision technology. RVT has worked hard to develop their world-class robotics support systems and now, working in partnership with IDF, they will take their innovations to new markets worldwide.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2992\" alignment=\"right\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1443728939975{margin-right: 20px !important;}\"]\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“By gaining access to IDF\'s global network of inventors, as well as the company\'s international footprint, RVT technologies can now get into the hands of even more leading companies around the world.” </em></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">— Rick Weidinger, RVT Founder and CEO</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Robotic VISION Technologies','','publish','open','closed','','small-to-mid-robotic-vision-technologies','','','2016-05-24 12:08:12','2016-05-24 19:08:12','',0,'http://inventiondevfund.com/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=2828',0,'portfolio','',0),(2829,1,'2015-09-08 23:09:24','2015-09-08 23:09:24','','Home-Thumb','','inherit','open','closed','','home-thumb-3','','','2015-09-08 23:09:24','2015-09-08 23:09:24','',2828,'http://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Home-Thumb.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2830,1,'2015-09-08 23:09:36','2015-09-08 23:09:36','','Home-Thumb-blackwhite','','inherit','open','closed','','home-thumb-blackwhite','','','2015-09-08 23:09:36','2015-09-08 23:09:36','',0,'http://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Home-Thumb-blackwhite.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2831,1,'2015-09-08 23:13:35','2015-09-08 23:13:35','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WEARABLE TECHNOLOGY GETS A BOOST</h2>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Strategic partnership with IDF paves the way for greater innovation and worldwide commercialization of Boogio motion-sensor technology.</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>INNOVATION</h2>\r\nSeattle-based REFLX Labs is the creator of a pioneering wearable technology that captures and analyzes human activity with high precision and accuracy. Their flagship product, Boogio Bionic Foot Sensors, employs paper-thin sensors and tiny computers to track movement and enable hands-free control of the technology. This is the first wearable system that can sense gravitational forces on the body, inner balance, and 3D motion in real-time.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_video link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ubT-G-wMbp4\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" margin_bottom=\"-40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2979\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1442859326520{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1465591490977{margin-right: 10px !important;margin-left: 20px !important;}\"]\r\n<h2>COLLABORATION</h2>\r\nAs an emerging company seeking to accelerate development and maximize use of available resources, REFLX partnered with the Invention Development Fund (IDF). In this strategic relationship, IDF is helping REFLX in three primary areas: sourcing new inventions via IDF’s global inventor network; licensing other relevant inventions in the IDF portfolio; and partnering on business development to help find additional Boogio customers in new markets.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" fancy_edge=\"corner_down\" fancy_edge_size=\"lg\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" fancy_edge_t_color=\"#0e73a3\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441133988315{margin-top: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>GROWTH</h2>\r\nBy joining forces with IDF, REFLX Labs continues to build a strong foundation for innovation and collaboration that connects its technology with partners in numerous industries. IDF’s work with REFLX Labs is part of a series of strategic relationships with entrepreneurial start-up companies to expand their base of inventions, protect those innovations, and market the resulting products around the world.\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2835\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">“<em>Working with IDF, I\'ve been advised by a team of engineers, business developers and IP strategists to identify challenges and opportunities in this competitive marketplace. We now have the resources and expertise to accelerate partnerships with developers and innovators.\"</em></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">— Jose Torres, CEO of REFLX Labs</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=