,'2016-03-18 21:26:54','',85,'https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Service-Icons-04.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(3490,1,'2016-03-22 10:24:26','2016-03-22 17:24:26','','Landing Pages','','publish','closed','closed','','lp','','','2016-03-22 10:24:26','2016-03-22 17:24:26','',0,'https://inventiondevfund.com/?page_id=3490',0,'page','',0),(3499,5,'2016-03-31 12:48:41','2016-03-31 19:48:41','','CMS Team 2015','','inherit','open','closed','','cms-team-2015','','','2016-03-31 12:48:41','2016-03-31 19:48:41','',3403,'https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/CMS-Team-2015.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(3500,5,'2016-04-02 11:36:40','2016-04-02 18:36:40','India-based Veol Medical Technologies is working in collaboration with the U.S.-based Invention Development Fund (IDF) to bring a new hair-transplant technology to the world. IDF is participating with securing international patents on the Veol-developed technology, and is also supporting expansion into global markets.\r\n\r\nThe company’s innovation addresses the estimated $1.8 B worldwide demand for quality hair transplant procedures and aligns with the market trend away from traditional surgical processes to a more effective method, known as Follicular Unit Extraction (FUE).  Their FUETOR™ automated hair transplant system offers multiple improvements in technology and performance results, including an expected 16% improvement in graft survival over competing methods.\r\n\r\nThe initial deployment of FUETOR units in India is providing empirical proof of performance as well as recognition from leading hair-transplant clinicians. Following the India-based launch, Veol is now pursuing broader opportunities for the new system.\r\n\r\nRegarding the collaborative relationship with IDF, Veol\'s CEO Mangesh Patankar said “IP protection is an important aspect of product development, without which we will not be able to reach out to world markets profitably. Participation of IDF helps FUETOR with IDF\'s vast experience, expertise, and reach in bringing good solutions to the global marketplace.”\r\n\r\nSimilarly, Satyajeet Parakh of IDF commented “We are pleased to have this opportunity to help provide new markets with FUETOR’s world-class technology which responds so well to a specific unmet need and elevates the standard of clinical care.”\r\n\r\nFor more information about FUETOR and Veol, please visit <a href=\"http://www.fuetor.com\">www.fuetor.com</a> and <a href=\"http://www.veollabs.com\">www.veollabs.com</a>. You can learn more about IDF at <a href=\"http://inventiondevfund.com/\">inventiondevfund.com</a>.','Invention Development Fund Assists Veol with Innovative Hair Transplant Technology to Address $1.8 B Worldwide Market','','publish','open','open','','veol-fuetor','','','2016-04-02 11:36:40','2016-04-02 18:36:40','',0,'https://inventiondevfund.com/?p=3500',0,'post','',0),(3502,5,'2016-04-01 12:09:03','2016-04-01 19:09:03','','Veol-Fuetor 02','','inherit','open','closed','','veol-fuetor-02','','','2016-04-01 12:09:03','2016-04-01 19:09:03','',0,'https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Veol-Fuetor-02.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(3505,1,'2016-04-06 15:19:05','2016-04-06 22:19:05','','invention-development-fund-5','','inherit','open','closed','','invention-development-fund-5','','','2016-04-06 15:19:05','2016-04-06 22:19:05','',85,'https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/invention-development-fund-5.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(3508,4,'2016-06-06 17:33:11','2016-06-07 00:33:11','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" padding_bottom=\"-80\" margin_bottom=\"-80\"][vc_column offset=\"vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md vc_hidden-sm\"][vc_single_image image=\"3759\" alignment=\"center\" link=\"#first\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"60\" padding_bottom=\"40\" font_color=\"#4d4d4d\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042963431{background-color: #f6f6f6 !important;}\"][vc_co