stom\" bg_color=\"custom\" bg_custom_color=\"#f6f6f6\" height=\"141\"]\r\n<h3><em>\"IDF has enabled me to become a full time inventor. It’s really a boyhood dream come true”</em></h3>\r\n[/om_box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][om_box border_width=\"0\" bg_color=\"custom\" bg_custom_color=\"#f6f6f6\"]\r\n<h2>DON\'T MISS AN OPPORTUNITY</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3555\" src=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/email.png\" alt=\"email\" width=\"166\" height=\"155\" />\r\n<div>Sign-up to receive the latest invention opportunities and news related to our inventor community.</div>\r\n[gravityform id=\"4\" title=\"false\"][/om_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][om_box border_width=\"0\" bg_color=\"custom\" bg_custom_color=\"#f6f6f6\" text_color=\"#424d3a\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-transform: uppercase;\">About Our Community</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3554 size-full\" src=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/network-2.png\" alt=\"network-2\" width=\"135\" height=\"154\" />\r\n\r\nIVIN is a collaborative community of scientific and technical experts, inventors, researchers, and entrepreneurs working together to create, improve, evaluate, and commercialize inventions. Members can review our ‘Requests for Invention’ (RFI), submit their inventions for selection and patenting or get paid for reviewing new inventions, analyzing existing patents, consulting or inviting other inventors to join IVIN.[/om_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][om_box border_width=\"0\" bg_color=\"custom\" bg_custom_color=\"#f6f6f6\"]\r\n<h2>INVENTOR COMMUNITY BLOG</h2>\r\n<a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/category/inventor-community/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3552 size-thumbnail\" src=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/blogging-150x150.png\" alt=\"blogging\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n\r\nSee what\'s happening in our inventor community.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/category/inventor-community/\">READ MORE &gt;</a>[/om_box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1463525907541{margin-top: 80px !important;}\" offset=\"vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md vc_hidden-sm\"][vc_single_image image=\"3556\" img_size=\"medium\" alignment=\"center\" link=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/invention-opportunity-non-thermal-pasteurization/\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"3/4\" offset=\"vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md vc_hidden-sm\"][om_click_icon_box2 icon_type=\"openiconic\" icon_openiconic=\"vc-oi vc-oi-quote-left\" title=\"INVENTOR SPOTLIGHT\"]Professional isolation is not good for the inventor’s soul. I find collaborating with other IVIN members often leads to better ideas, in fact, some of my recruits have become co-authors on inventions I’ve subsequently sold to Intellectual Ventures. For me, getting to focus on idea generation and leave the IP protection to someone else is a great opportunity to invent in realms I could not access otherwise. I credit more than half of my income and much of my success to Intellectual Ventures. There’s no other company besides IV that buys ideas from independent innovators.\r\n_\r\nDr. Shmuel Ur\r\nFull-time Inventor and CEO of Shmuel Ur Innovations Ltd.\r\n\r\n[/om_click_icon_box2][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1463531052210{margin-bottom: -80px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1463530949938{margin-bottom: -40px !important;}\"]\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 52px;\">COMMUNITY SPOTLIGHT</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\"][vc_column][rev_slider_vc alias=\"highlight-rfi-home\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Inventor Homepage','','publish','closed','closed','','inventors','','','