 Analysis</h4>\n</li>\n	<li class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Flawless Interpretation of Micro-Expression Data</h4>\n</li>\n	<li class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Automate Systems for Facial Recognition</h4>\n</li>\n	<li class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">Refinement and Automation of FACS</h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"3181\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"0\" padding_bottom=\"40\" font_color=\"#4d4d4d\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042963431{background-color: #f6f6f6 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][om_moving_box content_type=\"icon\" icon_type=\"typicons\" icon_size=\"54px\" icon_typicons=\"typcn typcn-arrow-down\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" css_animation_delay=\"200\" css=\".vc_custom_1449100474973{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 70px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 52px; text-transform: uppercase;\"><span style=\"color: #194265;\">WHY</span> <strong><span style=\"color: #ff940e;\">INVENT WITH US?</span></strong></h2>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_text_separator title=\"We Promote Innovation Through A Global Community of Inventors\" color=\"custom\" border_width=\"2\" el_width=\"50\" accent_color=\"#194265\" el_class=\"reduce-margin-top\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" css=\".vc_custom_1449023373109{margin-bottom: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"3114\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: 500;\"><span style=\"color: #194265;\">Global Community</span></h3>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Collaborate with an international community of inventors</h4>\n</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Have your inventions evaluated and potentially licensed</h4>\n</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Explore new realms for invention with industry defined problems to be solved</h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"3116\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: 500;\"><span style=\"color: #194265;\">Financial Reward</span></h3>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Receive upfront payments and patenting for selected inventions</h4>\n</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Share in profits and royalties from licensing and commercialization</h4>\n</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Gain opportunities for technical development funding</h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"3127\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: 500;\"><span style=\"color: #194265;\">Focus on Inventing</span></h3>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Ability to concentrate on research, development and the invention process</h4>\n</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Receive help securing patents and commercially promoting your inventions</h4>\n</li>\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<h4>Gain international exposure through our established networks</h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Bill-Walsh.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-3128 aligncenter\" src=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Bill-Walsh.png\" alt=\"Bill-Walsh\" width=\"250\" height=\"248\" /></a></p>\n<em>\"Working with the Invention Development Fund (IDF), is like working with a personal trainer. IDF provides the motivation as well as intellectual environment to get the best of our team. They have challenged us to provide the solutions and supported these ideas through a thorough understanding of the intellectual property landscape.”</em>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">_</p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Professor Bill Walsh</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Inventor and Lead Researcher</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">University of New South Wales</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Sydney, Australia</div>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Shmuel-Ur.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3130\" src=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Shmuel-Ur.png\" alt=\"Shmuel-Ur\" width=\"250\" height=\"248\" /></a></p>\n<em>\"Professional isolation is not good for the inventor’s soul. I find collaborating with other IVIN members often leads to better ideas, in fact, some of my recruits have become co-authors on inventions I\'ve subsequently sold to Intellectual Ventures. For me, getting to focus on idea generation and leave the IP protection to someone else is a great opportunity to invent in realms I could not access otherwise. I credit more than half of my income and much of my success to Intellectual Ventures. There’s no other company besides IV that buys ideas from independent innovators.\"</em>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">_</p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Dr. Shmuel Ur</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Full-time Inventor and</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">CEO of Shmuel Ur Innovations Ltd.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Shorashim, Israel</div>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Mike-Manion.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-3129 aligncenter\" src=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Mike-Manion.png\" alt=\"Mike-Manion\" width=\"250\" height=\"248\" /></a></p>\n<em>\"I started inventing with IVIDF about 5 years ago and it\'s allowed me to build my company. I started inventing alone on nights and weekends, but now, because of the work we do with IDF, it\'s allowed me to hire inventors, train people on inventing and build a lab where we can basically prototype anything we want to. IDF has enabled me to become a full time inventor. It\'s really a boyhood dream come true.\"</em>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">_</p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Dr. Michael Manion</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Full-time Inventor and</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">CEO of Keon Research</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Seattle, USA</div>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1449608302737{margin-bottom: -50px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][om_moving_box content_type=\"icon\" icon_type=\"typicons\" icon_size=\"54px\" icon_typicons=\"typcn typcn-arrow-down\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" padding_top=\"-10\" font_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_bottom=\"-10\" bg_color=\"#194265\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" delimiter=\"vline\" css=\".vc_custom_1449953324432{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1463593210857{margin-left: 10px !important;}\"]\n<h1 class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\">GET STARTED TODAY!</h1>\n<h3 class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Join today to receive further information on this invention opportunity, or to submit your invention for consideration.</h3>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"SIGN UP NOW!\" color=\"custom\" size=\"xlg\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:https%3A%2F%2Fivin.intven.com%2Fsignup|title:IVIN%20Sign%20Up|target:%20_blank\" custom_color=\"#ff940e\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1449953371424{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #658dc6 !important;}\" el_class=\"question-form\"][vc_column_text]\n<h1 class=\"p1\">HAVE A QUESTION?</h1>\n[/vc_column_text][gravityform id=\"3\" ajax=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_type=\"image\" bg_image_pos=\"cover\" padding_top=\"140\" padding_bottom=\"140\" font_color=\"#212121\" css=\".vc_custom_1441058056647{padding-top: 70px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-image: url(http://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Home-About-Background4.jpg) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\" bg_image=\"2967\"][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1449090389402{margin-bottom: 0px !important;border-bottom-width: 0px !important;}\" el_class=\"about_us\"]\n<h1 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ABOUT US</h1>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1441049736683{margin-top: -30px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"5/12\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/12\"][vc_separator color=\"custom\" border_width=\"3\" el_width=\"60\" accent_color=\"#7bc142\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"5/12\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1450118699238{margin-top: 0px !important;border-top-width: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}\"]\n<p class=\"p2\">The Invention Development Fund was established in 2007 as a new part of the Intellectual Ventures family of Investment Funds focused on building a global inventor network. IDF invents on behalf of its many customers in a variety of industries, ranging from huge multinational food and beverage or credit card companies to startups and regional Small &amp; Medium Enterprises (SMEs). IDF cultivates working relationships with inventors worldwide through its 10,000-strong global invention network (IVIN).</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1449090664800{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"JOIN OUR INVENTOR COMMUNITY\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" link=\"url:https%3A%2F%2Fivin.intven.com%2Fsignup||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]','WE HAVE AN INVENTION OPPORTUNITY FOR YOU!','','inherit','closed','closed','','3103-autosave-v1','','','2016-05-18 10:40:20','2016-05-18 17:40:20','',3103,'https://inventiondevfund.com/3103-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3579,5,'2016-05-19 19:29:14','2016-05-20 02:29:14','[vc_row][vc_column][om_posts mode=\"masonry\" columns=\"3\" hide_excerpt=\"yes\" title=\"Content You Might Enjoy While You Wait for a Response\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_btn][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"”#”\">CLICK ME</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"”HYPERLINK\">CLICK ME</a>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_raw_html]\r\n\r\nJTNDZGl2JTIwaWQlM0QlMjJjaGFydF9kaXYlMjIlM0UlM0MlMkZkaXYlM0UlMEE=\r\n\r\n[/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Test Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','3320-autosave-v1','','','2016-05-19 19:29:14','2016-05-20 02:29:14','',3320,'https://inventiondevfund.com/3320-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3580,5,'2016-05-24 16:38:18','2016-05-24 23:38:18','[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]CONFIDENTIAL. INTERNAL USE ONLY.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><em>What do we call ourselves now -- internally and externally?\r\n</em></strong>Please continue to use the IDF name for the immediate future. Our marketing team is working on a rebrand strategy and we expect to have a new company name and logo within 90 days from closing. (While in transition, we may also refer to ourselves internally as IX or Innovation X.)\r\n\r\n<strong><em>What can I say publicly about the transition?\r\n</em></strong>We prefer not to draw attention to this change until we roll out our new brand in a few months. Do not change the way you talk about our organization. A <a href=\"http://www.intellectualventures.com/insights/archives/looking-to-the-future-idf-in-transition\" target=\"_blank\">short post</a> was published on the IV Insights blog to serve as a response for any inquiries during the interim.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Do we still refer to Intellectual Ventures in any way?\r\n</em></strong>We are now a separate company and are working to expediently remove references to IV from our website content, marketing collateral, etc.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Can I use the existing marketing materials I have on hand?\r\n</em></strong>While it may be impractical to completely remove IV references from all materials, we ask that you apply the interim IDF-only templates when possible. They are available <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/sh/4wk7voqrj1izl4d/AABaNbqVnqrDJOvxUrZj42bta?dl=0\">here</a>. And similarly, where feasible, please swap in the non-IV version of the IDF logo, available <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/sh/xa3dm9kbbx2api8/AACwyJ6zAxGKwbJ9lWuz8Tc_a?dl=0\">here</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>What about my email identity?\r\n</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Our email addresses will remain on “@</span>intven.com<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">” for the near term. Please be sure to implement the interim IDF-only email signature block that was provided in a message from IDF Marketing on May 19.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>What about business cards. Do we need to reprint?\r\n</strong>We will reprint new business cards only after our new brand identity has been established. If needed, you may use your existing (IV-identified) business cards. Do so with appropriate discretion -- as we are already working to remove the IV identity from all other materials.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Will our overall mission remain the same?\r\n</em></strong>Our overall lines of business will stay the same. We will, however, aim to greatly increase the number of deals we close, including an increase in Sponsored Innovation deals and a return to doing SME deals. We also aim to drive more operational efficiencies from the spinout.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>What are our short-term priorities?\r\n</em></strong>Our short-term priorities are: execute rebranding; scale up deal activity; and execute the operational spinout from IV.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Is there an organization chart available?\r\n</em></strong>We are working on creating an org chart and will make it available soon.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Will my benefits change?\r\n</em></strong>In APAC countries, there is no change to benefits. In the US, we are contracting for new benefits effective June 1.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>How will I access my 401k?\r\n</em></strong>For US employees, our 401k accounts will stay at Fidelity, but are scheduled to migrate control groups internally within Fidelity during the month of July. We will provide more information as the schedule and effects are determined.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>When will we see the details of the various compensation programs (bonus plan, LTCIP replacement, IDF shares replacement)?\r\n</em></strong>We are working on all of these and will communicate the details when available, but we cannot commit to a date at this time.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Will there be an employee stock option or equity plan?\r\n</em></strong>If and when a stock-option plan is formed, additional information will be provided.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>The offer letters for US employees mention unlimited paid time off. What will happen with my accrued an unused IV time off? My current balance? How do I request time off under this new program?\r\n</em></strong>For US employees, we are moving to a flexible time-off policy, where allowed by local law, based upon company guidelines. We are drafting a written policy with guidelines, and will communicate this when it\'s ready. In other countries, the time-off policy remains unchanged, as required by local employment law.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Will our current facility access change?\r\n</em></strong>APAC offices will not move. The US team will eventually need to move. However, we will be subleasing our current space for several months, to allow us time to find and move into a new space. During that time, access to the Sunset office and surrounding facilities should continue unchanged.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>When are we planning on moving the US office, and to what city?\r\n</em></strong>The US-based team will eventually need to move out of the IV Sunset Building, though we currently have an extendable sub-lease to stay in place for at least 90 days. We are actively exploring leasing options in Seattle and downtown Bellevue. It will take several weeks to move into negotiations with landlords and make a space selection.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Who do I contact for technical support?\r\n</em></strong>For now, please continue to use the IV STG helpdesk process that you would normally use.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Will my email and system access change?\r\n</em></strong>Nothing will change right away. We have negotiated a transition services agreement with IV that allows for many support processes to continue status quo while we work to stand up its own systems and processes. This agreement lasts for six months and is extendable. We will eventually migrate all aspects of our IT and network infrastructure, including our web properties and email address domains. Ther will be different effects and schedules for each country. If you have detailed questions, please contact Joni Wyckoff or Matt Brock.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Are we able to keep our current computers/hardware?\r\n</em></strong>Yes.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>How do I submit business expenses?\r\n</em></strong>In APAC countries, the business expense submittal process is unchanged. For the US, IX Finance (Ross Thomas) is working on this, and they will update US team members shortly.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>How do I book travel?\r\n</em></strong>In APAC countries, the travel booking process is unchanged. In the US, you may continue to use Egencia if you choose, or you can book directly. The key thing is to shop around and use good judgement.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>What happens to my company credit card?\r\n</em></strong>In APAC countries, there is no change. In the US, new Silicon Valley Bank MasterCards have been ordered and should arrive to the Bellevue office no later than the week of May 23. Remote staff will receive these at their home addresses. Please direct any questions to Ross Thomas.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf you have any additional questions, please contact your manager or our HR representative: <a href=\"mailto:lorraine@swifthrsolutions.com\">lorraine@swifthrsolutions.com</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nCONFIDENTIAL. INTERNAL USE ONLY.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','IDF-IX Transition Q&A','','publish','closed','closed','','transition-faq','','','2016-06-02 09:04:57','2016-06-02 16:04:57','',0,'https://inventiondevfund.com/?page_id=3580',0,'page','',0),(3582,2,'2016-05-20 11:31:18','2016-05-20 18:31:18','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WEARABLE TECHNOLOGY GETS A BOOST</h2>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Strategic partnership with IDF paves the way for greater innovation and worldwide commercialization of Boogio motion-sensor technology.</h4>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>INNOVATION</h2>\nSeattle-based REFLX Labs is the creator of a pioneering wearable technology that captures and analyzes human activity with high precision and accuracy. Their flagship product, Boogio Bionic Foot Sensors, employs paper-thin sensors and tiny computers to track movement and enable hands-free control of the technology. This is the first wearable system that can sense gravitational forces on the body, inner balance, and 3D motion in real-time.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_video link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ubT-G-wMbp4\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" margin_bottom=\"-40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2979\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1442859326520{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1463769050066{margin-right: 10px !important;margin-left: 20px !important;}\"]\n<h2>COLLABORATION</h2>\nAs an emerging company seeking to accelerate development and maximize use of available resources, REFLX partnered with Invention Development Fund (IDF). In this strategic relationship, IDF is helping REFLX in three primary areas: sourcing new inventions via IDF’s global inventor network; licensing other relevant inventions in the IDF portfolio; and partnering on business development to help find additional Boogio customers in new markets.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" fancy_edge=\"corner_down\" fancy_edge_size=\"lg\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" fancy_edge_t_color=\"#0e73a3\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441133988315{margin-top: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>GROWTH</h2>\nBy joining forces with IV, REFLX Labs continues to build a strong foundation for innovation and collaboration that connects its technology with partners in numerous industries. IV’s work with REFLX Labs is part of a series of strategic relationships with entrepreneurial start-up companies to expand their base of inventions, protect those innovations, and market the resulting products around the world.\n<h3></h3>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2835\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h2></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">“<em>Working with IDF, I\'ve been advised by a team of engineers, business developers and IP strategists to identify challenges and opportunities in this competitive marketplace. We now have the resources and expertise to accelerate partnerships with developers and innovators.\"</em></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">— Jose Torres, CEO of REFLX Labs</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','REFLX Labs – Boogio','','inherit','closed','closed','','2831-autosave-v1','','','2016-05-20 11:31:18','2016-05-20 18:31:18','',2831,'https://inventiondevfund.com/2831-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3583,2,'2016-05-20 11:42:28','2016-05-20 18:42:28','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1463769695621{margin-top: 20px !important;}\"]\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">GAINING ACCESS TO INNOVATION</h2>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Global leader in paint and coatings teams up with IDF to explore potential for new product innovations.</h4>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>VISIONARY ENTERPRISE</h2>\nNetherlands-based AkzoNobel, the world’s largest paint and coatings company, is a major producer of specialty chemicals with a passionate emphasis on developing and delivering sustainable solutions to their customers. In line with their guiding philosophy of Tomorrow’s Answers Today™, AkzoNobel continually seeks new technologies to provide improved products to industries and consumers worldwide.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"3041\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" margin_bottom=\"-40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2824\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441134053801{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1442859976678{margin-right: 10px !important;margin-left: 20px !important;}\"]\n<h2>COOPERATIVE INNOVATION</h2>\nIn pursuit of new paint and coating technologies, AkzoNobel has been working cooperatively with the Invention Development Fund at Intellectual Ventures (IV). Through a joint collaboration agreement, the companies will work with the IV Invention Network of more than 10,000 inventors, research institutions and universities, to discover and develop potential new products. The partnership also provides AkzoNobel access to existing technologies in the IV portfolio of chemistry and materials science inventions.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" fancy_edge=\"corner_down\" fancy_edge_size=\"lg\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" fancy_edge_t_color=\"#0e73a3\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441133988315{margin-top: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>COMMERCIAL POTENTIAL</h2>\nThe benefits of this agreement for AkzoNobel include the option to expand upon discoveries generated through this project, allowing for future product development and commercialization opportunities. The working relationship with Intellectual Ventures provides AkzoNobel the potential for new coating technologies that will improve its competitive position in the global marketplace.\n<h3></h3>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2827\" img_size=\"large\" alignment=\"right\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“This collaboration with Intellectual Ventures aims to enhance the innovation pipelines available to AkzoNobel to help us achieve our goal of continued improvement and new product introductions.” </em></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>– </em>Jos Keurentjes, AkzoNobel Director of Open Innovation</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','AkzoNobel','','inherit','closed','closed','','2668-autosave-v1','','','2016-05-20 11:42:28','2016-05-20 18:42:28','',2668,'https://inventiondevfund.com/2668-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3584,2,'2016-05-20 11:45:24','2016-05-20 18:45:24','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">TAKING LOCAL INNOVATION GLOBAL</h2>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Finnish innovator in cattle-feed supplements sees global market benefits through a strategic partnership with IDF.</h4>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>NEW CATTLE FEED OFFERS WORLDWIDE BENEFITS</h2>\nRaisio, a leading European food production company, develops cattle-feed supplements that make milk production safer, more efficient, and more environmentally responsible. These innovative feeds, successfully launched to the Finnish Dairy industry as the Benemilk® product line, are now poised for international success through broader geographical licensing and IP augmentation.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_video link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yl9ocRrY4fo\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" margin_bottom=\"-40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2977\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441134053801{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1442859621077{margin-right: 10px !important;margin-left: 20px !important;}\"]\n<h2>JOINT VENTURE AGREEMENT ENABLES GLOBAL REACH</h2>\nTo obtain the necessary expertise and global reach, Raisio is working with Intellectual Ventures, a recognized world leader in strengthening IP portfolios and marketing new innovations. In ongoing partnership, they will seek to leverage the value of Raisio’s core technology via Intellectual Ventures’ global network of inventors and world-class patent and licensing know-how. The April 2013 announcement of a joint venture between Raisio and Intellectual Ventures’ Invention Development Fund transfers ownership of the original invention to a new jointly owned Finnish company, Benemilk® Oy.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" fancy_edge=\"corner_down\" fancy_edge_size=\"lg\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" fancy_edge_t_color=\"#0e73a3\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441133988315{margin-top: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>ONGOING YIELDS, ONGOING INNOVATION</h2>\nThe agreement provides Raisio with continued success in Finland along with the added benefit of introducing their invention to dairy markets worldwide. And Intellectual Ventures is also helping with the discovery and application of complementary innovations to further promote safe, efficient, and environmentally responsible food production.\n<h3></h3>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2976\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h2></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“Our work with IDF and its international invention ecosystem brings the best possible expertise and resources to bear upon the improvement, patenting, enforcement, and global commercialization of our inventions.” </em></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">— Raisio CEO Matti Rihko</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Raisio Benemilk','','inherit','closed','closed','','2650-autosave-v1','','','2016-05-20 11:45:24','2016-05-20 18:45:24','',2650,'https://inventiondevfund.com/2650-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3585,5,'2016-05-22 22:19:11','2016-05-23 05:19:11','Click to play an example \"Explainer\" video for IVIN recruitment.\r\n\r\n[video width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" mp4=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/90secondexplainervideos-IVIDF_vid2_V1.mp4\"][/video]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','IDF Team Sneak Preview: Explainer Video','','inherit','closed','closed','','3404-autosave-v1','','','2016-05-22 22:19:11','2016-05-23 05:19:11','',3404,'https://inventiondevfund.com/3404-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3586,5,'2016-05-23 08:31:04','2016-05-23 15:31:04','<strong>BELLEVUE, Washington, USA, OSAKA, Japan — May 23, 2016<em> —The Invention Development Fund (IDF) </em></strong>and <strong><em>Funai Electric</em></strong> announced today that the companies will collaborate in the field of new business development. Funai, a leading global manufacturer under the FUNAI and other multiple brands, will have its research and development staff collaborate with platinum level inventors in the IDF <em>Invention Network</em>, a global network of inventors, research institutes, universities, and companies.\r\n\r\nThe collaboration between Funai and IDF seeks to identify new applications and enter new markets based around the core capabilities and technologies Funai has achieved in developing its products.  The two companies will define topic areas suitable for collaboration and innovation.  The goal of the collaboration is to generate new technology solutions, inventions, and prototypes that will enable Funai to create new products and solutions.\r\n\r\n“Funai Electric is excited to explore new opportunities to apply our advanced product development and manufacturing capabilities with IDF. Our diverse patent portfolio and innovative core technologies uniquely position us to bring revolutionary solutions to a diverse field of applications,” said Joji Okada, Director &amp; Officer at Funai.\r\n\r\n“Funai Electric represents the best that Japanese manufacturing has to offer,” said Chris Alliegro, President &amp; Chief Operating Officer of the Invention Development Fund. “By joining forces with Funai to create new technical solutions, prototypes, and use-case scenarios for their existing technologies, we aim to invent the future and bring exciting new areas of technology into wider fields of use, such as in healthcare, greentech, and robotics.”\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>About Funai Electric</strong>\r\n\r\nFunai established in 1961, and headquartered in Osaka, Japan, is listed in the Tokyo Securities Exchange First Section (6839). It is a leading manufacturer of LCD TVs, DVDs/Blu-rays and related peripherals, printers, and antennas, and other items. It sells its products under the FUNAI brand name as well as other multiple brands in the global Consumer Electronics markets. Funai is also well known as a major Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) and Supplier. FUNAI products have a strong and solid global reputation for their quality and reasonable prices.\r\n\r\nFor more information on the Funai group, please visit <a href=\"http://www.funai.jp/en/index.html\">www.funai.jp/en/</a>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>About the Invention Development Fund</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Invention Development Fund (IDF) is a company of over 75 experts, including PhDs, product and commercialization experts, business analysts, and intellectual property experts operating in 8 countries around the world. IDF manages the <em>Invention Network</em>, a community of thousands of inventors residing at more than 400 companies, institutions, and universities worldwide. IDF’s client base of companies looking to find new technologies and inventions includes global Fortune 500 companies, small and medium sized enterprises, and start-ups.\r\n\r\nMore information about IDF is available via <a href=\"http://www.inventiondevfund.com\">inventiondevfund.com</a> or <a href=\"mailto:idf-marketing@intven.com\">idf-marketing@intven.com.\r\n</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','The Invention Development Fund and Funai Electric Announce New Collaboration','','publish','open','open','','idf-funai-collab','','','2016-05-23 08:31:04','2016-05-23 15:31:04','',0,'https://inventiondevfund.com/?p=3586',0,'post','',0),(3587,5,'2016-05-22 22:20:28','2016-05-23 05:20:28','','Funai IDF Group 01','','inherit','open','closed','','funai-idf-group-01','','','2016-05-22 22:20:47','2016-0