2:44:22','2016-06-08 19:44:22','',3508,'https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/transcriptionv22.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(3727,4,'2016-06-08 12:45:38','2016-06-08 19:45:38','','Costv2','','inherit','open','closed','','costv2','','','2016-06-08 12:45:38','2016-06-08 19:45:38','',3508,'https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Costv2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(3728,4,'2016-06-08 12:45:43','2016-06-08 19:45:43','','Costv22','','inherit','open','closed','','costv22','','','2016-06-08 12:45:43','2016-06-08 19:45:43','',3508,'https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Costv22.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(3729,4,'2016-06-08 12:45:48','2016-06-08 19:45:48','','Costv23','','inherit','open','closed','','costv23','','','2016-06-08 12:45:48','2016-06-08 19:45:48','',3508,'https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Costv23.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(3730,4,'2016-06-08 13:00:05','2016-06-08 20:00:05','','technology6','','inherit','open','closed','','technology6','','','2016-06-08 13:00:05','2016-06-08 20:00:05','',3508,'https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/technology6.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(3735,4,'2016-06-10 12:05:07','2016-06-10 19:05:07','<a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/2016.06.6_IDF-Inventor-Blog_Alyssa_Welcome-Inventors-Image.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-3737\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-3737\" src=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/2016.06.6_IDF-Inventor-Blog_Alyssa_Welcome-Inventors-Image-1024x481.jpg\" alt=\"Welcome Inventors\" width=\"1000\" height=\"470\" /></a>\r\n\r\nWelcome to our new “Inventor Community Blog” and our new inventor-focused landing page (<a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/inventors/\" target=\"_blank\">inventiondevfund.com/inventors</a>). We anticipate that these new platforms will greatly improve our connectivity with our global inventor community.\r\n\r\nThe new blog is a channel for sharing news, updates and inventor-related content, as well as a place for us to interact and engage with our inventor community. We welcome your feedback as we create new content.\r\n\r\nOur new inventor-focused landing page is designed to welcome new and existing inventors into our inventor community. On this page, we will share stories from inventors and staff within our community and showcase forthcoming Requests for Invention (RFIs).\r\n\r\nWe look forward to deepening our relationship with you, our inventors. We appreciate you stopping by our site and we encourage you to sign-up for our RSS feed and e-newsletters.\r\n\r\nThe IDF Inventor Community Staff','Welcome Inventors!','','publish','open','open','','welcome-inventors','','','2016-06-13 17:37:46','2016-06-14 00:37:46','',0,'https://inventiondevfund.com/?p=3735',0,'post','',0),(3737,4,'2016-06-10 12:03:11','2016-06-10 19:03:11','','Welcome Inventors!','','inherit','open','closed','','2016-06-6_idf-inventor-blog_alyssa_welcome-inventors-image','','','2016-06-10 12:03:34','2016-06-10 19:03:34','',3735,'https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/2016.06.6_IDF-Inventor-Blog_Alyssa_Welcome-Inventors-Image.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(3741,4,'2016-06-10 13:50:41','2016-06-10 20:50:41','','Animal Tracking | Current Technology','','inherit','open','closed','','tech-grid3v2','','','2016-06-10 13:51:08','2016-06-10 20:51:08','',3508,'https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Tech-Grid3v2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(3743,5,'2016-06-10 13:59:42','2016-06-10 20:59:42','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">TAKING LOCAL INNOVATION GLOBAL</h2>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Finnish innovator in cattle-feed supplements sees global market benefits through a strategic partnership with IDF.</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>NEW CATTLE FEED OFFERS WORLDWIDE BENEFITS</h2>\r\nRaisio, a leading European food production company, develops cattle-feed supplements that make milk production safer, more efficient, and more environmentally responsible. These innovative feeds, successfully launched to the Finnish Dairy industry as the Benemilk® product line, are now poised for international success through broader geographical licensing and IP augmentation.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_video link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yl9ocRrY4fo\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" margin_bottom=\"-40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2977\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441134053801{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1463769982210{margin-right: 10px !important;margin-left: 20px !important;}\"]\r\n<h2>JOINT VENTURE AGREEMENT ENABLES GLOBAL REACH</h2>\r\nTo obtain the necessary expertise and global reach, Raisio is working with IDF, a recognized leader in strengthening IP portfolios and marketing new innovations. In ongoing partnership, they will seek to leverage the value of Raisio’s core technology via IDF\'s global network of inventors and world-class patent and licensing know-how. The April 2013 announcement of a joint venture between Raisio and IDF transfers ownership of the original invention to a new jointly owned Finnish company, Benemilk® Oy.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" fancy_edge=\"corner_down\" fancy_edge_size=\"lg\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" fancy_edge_t_color=\"#0e73a3\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441133988315{margin-top: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>ONGOING YIELDS, ONGOING INNOVATION</h2>\r\nThe agreement provides Raisio with continued success in Finland along with the added benefit of introducing their invention to dairy markets worldwide. And IDF is also helping with the discovery and application of complementary innovations to further promote safe, efficient, and environmentally responsible food production.\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2976\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“Our work with IDF and its international invention ecosystem brings the best possible expertise and resources to bear upon the improvement, patenting, enforcement, and global commercialization of our inventions.” </em></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">— Raisio CEO Matti Rihko</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Raisio Benemilk','','inherit','closed','closed','','2650-autosave-v1','','','2016-06-10 13:59:42','2016-06-10 20:59:42','',2650,'https://inventiondevfund.com/2650-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3744,5,'2016-06-10 14:02:16','2016-06-10 21:02:16','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">LOOKING TO THE FUTURE OF MACHINE AUTOMATION</h2>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Industry leader in machine-vision systems prepares for global expansion with its best-in-class technology.</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"20\" padding_bottom=\"20\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1442861846634{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>THE RVT PLATFORM</h2>\r\nRobotic VISION Technologies (RVT), an independent software and support services company, develops software products that enable robots and other automated machines to “see, think, and do.” Advanced machine vision is a key factor for robotic systems to become more precise, reliable, and efficient. RVT’s software platform for vision-guided robotics supports applications in multiple industries, including automotive, materials handling, bottling, inspection, and general manufacturing.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"3040\" img_size=\"600x399\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" margin_bottom=\"-40\" padding_top=\"-40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2989\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1442862639554{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1463770070531{margin-right: 10px !important;margin-left: 20px !important;}\"]\r\n<h2>PARTNERSHIP WITH IDF</h2>\r\nRVT’s technology leadership and U.S.-based industry success positions the company for global growth. RVT partnered with IDF to expedite progress toward an increased international presence. Through this strategic partnership, RVT will gain access to IDF’s global network of inventors to collaborate on new robotics inventions. IDF will also help strengthen RVT’s existing patent portfolio and will introduce new markets and customers to RVT technology and software products.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" fancy_edge=\"corner_down\" fancy_edge_size=\"lg\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" fancy_edge_t_color=\"#0e73a3\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441133988315{margin-top: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>GLOBAL OPPORTUNITIES</h2>\r\nThe future is bright for RVT as the use of robotic technologies rapidly expands into new industries and applications, creating demand for advanced machine vision technology. RVT has worked hard to develop their world-class robotics support systems and now, working in partnership with IDF, they will take their innovations to new markets worldwide.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2992\" alignment=\"right\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1443728939975{margin-right: 20px !important;}\"]\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“By gaining access to IDF\'s global network of inventors, as well as the company\'s international footprint, RVT technologies can now get into the hands of even more leading companies around the world.” </em></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">— Rick Weidinger, RVT Founder and CEO</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Robotic VISION Technologies','','inherit','closed','closed','','2828-autosave-v1','','','2016-06-10 14:02:16','2016-06-10 21:02:16','',2828,'https://inventiondevfund.com/2828-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3745,5,'2016-06-10 14:05:54','2016-06-10 21:05:54','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">INNOVATION BRINGS NEW FOOD SOURCE TO LIFE</h2>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Transformative process provides nutritional, economic, and environmental benefits worldwide. The team behind Coffee Flour™ saw a long-standing problem in need of a solution and invented a process for turning the unvalued coffee cherry pulp cast off in the harvest of coffee beans into nutritious and tasty flour.</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>FRUITFUL OPPORTUNITY</h2>\r\nIn traditional processing, coffee beans are separated from coffee cherries, and the remaining fruit pulp is discarded. Every year, more than a billion pounds of this unused by- product is left to decompose, often causing unintended harm to local ecosystems. Seeking a solution to this ongoing problem, inventor Dan Belliveau began to develop a process that would convert the coffee cherry pulp into a new, all-natural food ingredient now known as Coffee Flour.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_video link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=9&amp;v=wKPUskVtGow\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" margin_bottom=\"-40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2572\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441134053801{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1463770207386{margin-right: 10px !important;}\"]\r\n<h2>COLLABORATIVE DEVELOPMENT</h2>\r\nBelliveau sought out partners who could help translate his early successes into a product for the global marketplace. He engaged the support of IDF who assisted with funding and legal issues, as well as practical product development activities, including nutritional analysis, ingredient testing, certifications, and test kitchen work. Collaboration led to the involvement of several key players in the food process supply chain, including distributors and grower-producer companies around the globe.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" fancy_edge=\"corner_down\" fancy_edge_size=\"lg\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" fancy_edge_t_color=\"#0e73a3\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441133988315{margin-top: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>SHARED BENEFITS</h2>\r\nNow carried forward by a newly formed company, CF Global Holdings Inc., the Coffee Flour innovation will provide fresh culinary possibilities to kitchens worldwide with a healthy, flavorful new food ingredient. This ecologically smart use of a formerly discarded byproduct not only adds to the food supply, but also offers improved income stability for small coffee farmers and their local economies.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2570\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1451961151592{margin-right: 35px !important;}\"]\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">“<em>Our partnership with IDF is providing the necessary elements to position us for ongoing success on a global scale.</em>”</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">— Dan Belliveau, CF Global Holdings Founder and CEO</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Finventiondevfund.com%2Fcontact-us%2F||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Coffee Flour','','inherit','closed','closed','','99-autosave-v1','','','2016-06-10 14:05:54','2016-06-10 21:05:54','',99,'https://inventiondevfund.com/99-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3746,4,'2016-06-13 16:02:49','2016-06-13 23:02:49','','Current Animal Tracking Technology | IDF','','inherit','open','closed','','tech-grid1v2','','','2016-06-13 16:03:39','2016-06-13 23:03:39','',3508,'https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Tech-Grid1v2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(3747,1,'2016-06-13 17:32:54','2016-06-14 00:32:54',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','3747','','','2016-06-29 13:24:03','2016-06-29 20:24:03','',0,'https://inventiondevfund.com/?p=3747',10,'nav_menu_item','',0),(3748,1,'2016-06-23 11:05:31','2016-06