ntion Development Fund (IDF) was established in 2007 to focus on building a global inventor network. IDF invents on behalf of its many customers in a variety of industries, ranging from huge multinational food and beverage or credit card companies to startups and regional Small &amp; Medium Enterprises (SMEs). IDF cultivates working relationships with inventors worldwide through its 10,000-strong global invention network.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1449090664800{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"JOIN OUR INVENTOR COMMUNITY\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" shape=\"square\" link=\"url:https%3A%2F%2Fivin.intven.com%2Fsignup||\" custom_color=\"#f78e18\" hover_custom_color=\"#dd9e40\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"]\n[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]','WE HAVE AN INVENTION OPPORTUNITY FOR YOU!','','inherit','closed','closed','','3103-autosave-v1','','','2016-06-17 11:45:14','2016-06-17 18:45:14','',3103,'https://inventiondevfund.com/3103-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3753,4,'2016-06-16 14:35:18','2016-06-16 21:35:18','<a href=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/2016.06.16_IVIN-Blog_Flying-Cars.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-3754\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-3754\" src=\"https://inventiondevfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/2016.06.16_IVIN-Blog_Flying-Cars-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"Flying Cars\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></a>\r\n\r\nGoogle co-founder, Larry Page seems to think so! He’s personally funding the start-up Zee.Aero and backing up Kitty Hawk, another start-ups focused on making flying cars. Many have chased this dream for decades without success. Is the future of the flying car finally becoming attainable or does it remain just a dream of the, \"growing body of smart, wealthy, and appar