text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>FOUNDATIONAL WORK</h2>\r\nEden Research develops natural micro-encapsulation technologies and terpene-derived products for the plant protection, animal health and human personal health markets worldwide. Terpenes are organic compounds derived from essential oils and the resin of pine trees and other plants. They provide many antibacterial, antifungal, and anti-microbial qualities. Terpene-derived pesticides can naturally protect crops from common plant diseases or pests. Other uses include using terpene-derived anti-microbial products for animal health, personal care, oral care, and general household products.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"3788\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" bg_color=\"#f2ede9\" margin_bottom=\"-40\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"3790\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441134053801{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1467253959723{margin-right: 10px !important;margin-left: 20px !important;}\"]\r\n<h2>EXPANDING POSSIBILITIES</h2>\r\nBuilding on the momentum of their breakthrough technologies, Eden entered into collaboration with the Seattle-based Invention Development Fund (IDF) to further accelerate their progress. IDF provides a depth of world-leading IP-related services and a global network of licensing and business-development professionals. The agreement leverages the natural synergies of IDF’s experience in agricultural, animal health, food ingredients, human health, and personal-care markets.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" fancy_edge=\"corner_down\" fancy_edge_size=\"lg\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" fancy_edge_t_color=\"#0e73a3\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1441133988315{margin-top: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>GOING FORWARD TOGETHER</h2>\r\nEden now gains the benefit of possible licensing opportunities from IDF’s portfolio of existing IP assets as well as access to IDF’s global invention network – a community of more than 10,000 members from whom valuable innovations may be obtained to enhance Eden’s core technologies. IDF will also assist Eden with expansion into new geographies around the world, with a particular emphasis on market expansion in Asia, North America, and South America. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"3793\" img_size=\"large\" alignment=\"right\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em> “Eden will utilise IDF’s unique “invention engine” to enhance and extend our core intellectual property portfolio and expand our technology base in areas outside of our current focus. IDF’s global presence will also help us to increase our market presence outside Europe more efficiently and rapidly.”</em></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>– </em>Sean Smith, Eden CEO</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">To learn more about Eden, please visit <a href=\"http://www.edenresearch.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.edenresearch.com</a></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" padding_bottom=\"50\" css=\".vc_custom_1441042786961{margin-bottom: -40px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #8ec549 !important;}\" bg_color=\"#0e73a3\" padding_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" delimiter=\"vline\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">READY TO START THE CONVERSATION?</span></h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" css=\".vc_custom_1440811513097{margin-top: 17px !important;}\"][vc_btn title=\"LET\'S TALK!\" color=\"custom\" hover_color=\"custom\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" sh