u work with all type of ideas?'),(860,'I am looking for a snacks for south indians to be used as mini with a shelf life of 3-5 days. If you have some suggestion it can be considered. I have some suggestions also which will be informed you later.\r\n\r\nRegards, Pushkaran\r\ntvpush@gmail.com\r\n9633260174'),(865,'i consider myself a person with great ideas in my head.i always do my own search trhu the internet and going to stores.right now i have and idea that i believe can solve one of tne biggest problem in the auto industry....auto theft.my question is, do you work with all type of ideas?'),(871,'Hi,\r\n\r\nI am Peter, an inventor from Kenya\r\nI have a good invention, but I am stuck in the invention process. Kindly assist me so that I can move forward. \r\n\r\nLooking forward to your response.\r\n\r\nRegards.'),(876,'Hi,\r\n\r\nI am Peter, an inventor from Kenya\r\nI have a good invention, but I am stuck in the invention process. Kindly assist me so that I can move forward. \r\n\r\nLooking forward to your response.\r\n\r\nRegards.'),(881,'we working in india among startups and promoting ip , we are receiving lot enquires regarding funding of international application, we are looking for organisation who can help us in collaboration, we can take care of legal side.\r\n\r\nwww.ipforstartup.com\r\n\r\nyou can reach us on +919205385276'),(886,'Hi, I\'m very keen to connect with you to explore being part of IDF community. My Singapore mobile is +65 96725291. \r\n\r\nUnfortunately, I will miss the June 29th, 30th CIO Summit in Singapore as I\'d be travelling to Vancouver during that period.\r\n\r\nHowever, you can reach me either on mobile or email (deepakgunvante@gmail.com). Thanks & Regards, Deepak'),(894,'I have developed a transformational edibles technology where I have reduced ie: THC/CBD  effective medical dosage rate for edibles , cannabis, other herbs, etc by a factor of from 5 to 6 times.   Also, I have proved that I can made a coffee/cappuchino edibles culinary tech where   consumer feels the effect of my culinary tech cannabis in cappuccino/coffee within a period of 10 seconds to 30 seconds; very very fact perception of medication due to my personally developed high tech culinary extremely low dose edibles technology.  The tech is good for other herbs, etc besides cannabis.'),(897,'I have developed a transformational edibles technology where I have reduced ie: THC/CBD  effective medical dosage rate for edibles , cannabis, other herbs, etc by a factor of from 5 to 6 times.   Also, I have proved that I can made a coffee/cappuchino edibles culinary tech where   consumer feels the effect of my culinary tech cannabis in cappuccino/coffee within a period of 10 seconds to 30 seconds; very very fact perception of medication due to my personally developed high tech culinary extremely low dose edibles technology.  The tech is good for other herbs, etc besides cannabis.'),(927,'Quite sometime back I had received mail from you regarding development of technology.\r\n     I am writing this mail for some kind help from you, if possible.\r\n\r\n    Few years back I worked as a research scientist  based on project from DST, Govt. of India. The work was carried out in Indian Institute of Technology, Bombay.  After the project ended I worked on synthesis of coated magnetite nano particles with bio compatible molecules of amino acids on my own. It is in suspension for about 2 years. I have not published this work. I can send measurements like VSM;  and ICP,TEM , FTIR if necessary. The coated particles have 55 emu/gm magnetization after about 2 yr.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nIn the field of  ferrofluids toxicity  and suspension stability are of utmost importance. Since our coating is 100% natural, and suspension being stable for about 2 yr., both the issues are very well taken care of, and the suspension should be acceptable for biomedical and industrial applications.\r\n               \r\n        I wish to explore the possibility of technology transfer and know the about various aspects and requirements. \r\n\r\n\r\n   With  thanks and regards\r\n    Awaiting your reply'),(933,'I am scheduled to meet Erick Rabins on Wednesday next week at IDF and would like to discuss the meeting with him.  I am contemplating bringing another person with me, but want to check with him first.  I do not have his phone number because the meeting was arranged by others.  Please send me his phone number or email.\r\n\r\nMany Thanks,\r\nJohn Preston'),(938,'I have innovated the Design of small ship (DUMB BARGE - SHIP WITHOUT ENGINE POWER). with Green containers to load cargoes. This is very useful for INLAND WATER TRANSPORT. How u can help me to convert into a PRODUCT? \r\nTks.'),(954,'Hi\r\n\r\nI am interested in exploring opportunities as a consultant or inventor with IDF (in my personal capacity).\r\n\r\nI am a professor of computer science at NC State University and am an (co)inventor of 15 patents. You can find some more information, including my CV on my university site: https://www.csc.ncsu.edu/faculty/mpsingh/\r\n\r\nPlease let me know if you would like to discuss further.\r\n\r\nSincerely\r\nMunindar Singh, Ph.D.\r\nProfessor'),(959,'Hi\r\n\r\n[Correction]\r\n\r\nI am interested in exploring opportunities as a consultant or inventor with IDF (in my personal capacity).\r\n\r\nI am a professor of computer science at NC State University and am an (co)inventor of 14 patents. You can find some more information, including my CV on my university site: https://www.csc.ncsu.edu/faculty/mpsingh/\r\n\r\nPlease let me know if you would like to discuss further.\r\n\r\nSincerely\r\nMunindar Singh, Ph.D.\r\nProfessor'),(1000,'I live in Bangalore, India. I have done my Four Years Bachelors in Engineering in Food Preservation and Processing Technology. I have industry experience of around 4 years in various positions, including Product Development. I wish to undertake Projects in Food Processing, Safety and New Product Development. \r\nPlease let me know how do we take this forward.');
